<p class="">Would the Chancellor of the Exchequer allow me to—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d0903bcf-b270-4bf3-900f-199cb3ea5b1c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
